            "title": "【機構發債潮解析】國泰機管局籌逾百億：分散風險定借新還舊？ 一文看清發債利弊與經濟啟示",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EyFSPzeIMoy439APkhyskg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/28hse_com_210/459e7e620b548544661deab4e0549bd5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
