        },
        {
            "title": "新世界核心區甲廈出租率逾九成 「83 永康街」錄10宗買賣涉資逾億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/M24e4UC0P07FzqR4hv8TJg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/bf5772b1abea3ba0d2818f6018090f12\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
